<i>noun</i>: 노망 [노ː망] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>노망 [노ː망]</dt><br>
<dd>dotage; senility</dd><br>
<dd>늙어서 정신이 흐려지고 말이나 행동이 정상이 아닌 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a person's mental acuity is weak and his/her words and behavior are abnormal as a result of old age.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>